OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA touch of frost first thing in
OL,6,Fthe morning for some. It will then be
OL,7,Fa dry and bright day with a few rather
OL,8,Fhazy sunny spells between patchy cloud.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FDry, bright with hazy
OL,11,Fsunshine this evening. The rest of the
OL,12,Fnight will be predominately dry,
OL,13,Fhowever a few showers may develop
OL,14,Facross Dumfries and Galloway in the
OL,15,Fearly hours.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FA bright, partly cloudy day
OL,18,Fwith hazy sunny spells. Occasional
OL,19,Fshowers will develop and spread
OL,20,Fnortheast through the day, some may be
OL,21,Fon the heavy side.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
